00:07:20,841 --> 00:07:21,921
We didn't have a QA team.

120
00:07:21,981 --> 00:07:23,662
We didn't have, you know, like a support line.

121
00:07:23,982 --> 00:07:26,863
It was, it was just, it was practically a bunch of guys,

122
00:07:27,343 --> 00:07:30,063
you know, like in a, in a, in a garage band setup.

123
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:37,462
And so it's given us the time and by working through early access

124
00:07:37,522 --> 00:07:40,824
and putting out a lot of updates, it's given us...

125
00:07:42,465 --> 00:07:45,827
The process of early access for us on Astroneer has been as much

126
00:07:46,387 --> 00:07:50,610
to build system era and learn how to be system era as it has to build the game.

127
00:07:51,490 --> 00:07:54,912
Right on. Yeah, I mean, it was ages ago, but I remember we did an interview with you guys

