00:08:00,179 --> 00:08:03,942
And if I remember right, most of the team came from sort of big budget productions,

131
00:08:03,962 --> 00:08:07,685
you know, they came from, I think, 343 and such, you know, AAA developers.

132
00:08:07,765 --> 00:08:08,325
All of us, yeah.

133
00:08:08,586 --> 00:08:08,866
Yeah.

134
00:08:09,666 --> 00:08:11,708
I wonder, like, now that you sort of have this shipped,

